---
title: Cheesy Smokey Beef Quesadillas with Corn-Radish Salsa & Yoghurt
description: It’s the classic quesadillas again except we’re spicing things up with our fan-favourite all-American spice to coat the rich beef mince. Make it a little cheesy and add a golden corn salsa to tie it all together.
